A lot of people say, "Well, did God put sickness on you?

00:27:16.080 --> 00:27:18.159
" God doesn't put sickness on people.

00:27:36.205 --> 00:27:36.468
I don't believe it.

00:27:57.001 --> 00:27:58.108
The devil comes to kill, steal, and destroy.

00:28:02.310 --> 00:28:11.940
The Lord said, "I have come that you might have life and life more abundantly.

00:28:11.940 --> 00:28:15.550
" God doesn't put sickness on people.

00:28:15.550 --> 00:28:18.720
I do not believe that.

00:28:18.720 --> 00:28:36.809
We live in a fallen world and things happen, but I don't believe that God and the devil are working as buddies putting stuff on people.

00:28:50.320 --> 00:28:50.540
He was off balance here.

00:28:50.540 --> 00:28:53.860
I'll let him have a little cancer.

00:28:53.860 --> 00:29:06.464
Satan and him are not buddying up, slapping his bride around, slapping the church around, slapping people around.

00:29:07.112 --> 00:29:07.544
I don't believe it.

00:29:07.544 --> 00:29:12.289
You'll never convince me of it.

00:29:25.070 --> 00:29:25.260
The Bible says that God has come that we might have life and life more abundantly.

00:29:25.260 --> 00:29:27.836
What about your daughter Megan?

00:29:27.836 --> 00:29:32.880
What about that?

00:30:01.749 --> 00:30:02.279
That was my own stupid fault.

00:30:02.279 --> 00:30:15.679
He told me not to get the flu shot whenever I did it.

00:30:23.800 --> 00:30:24.230
Her Apgar scores were completely normal.

00:30:24.230 --> 00:30:28.389
She was starting to talk, doing everything.

00:31:01.679 --> 00:31:01.987
And within just a couple weeks of getting that flu vaccination, she ran a high fever and she lost all talking.

00:31:01.987 --> 00:31:08.079
Within just a couple weeks, she stopped looking at us in the eyes.

00:31:08.079 --> 00:31:15.279
She started looking over and being in la-la land.

00:31:41.759 --> 00:31:42.159
It was awful.

00:31:42.159 --> 00:32:02.811
And I'll never forget getting that letter in the mail certified from the doctor firing us as patients, telling us not to come back because we were saying we believe it's the flu vaccines.

00:32:02.811 --> 00:32:06.260
We believe all these things.

00:32:06.260 --> 00:32:08.080
She said don't come back.

00:32:08.080 --> 00:32:21.618
She fired us as patients and wouldn't let it go.

00:32:21.618 --> 00:32:28.658
I remember getting that FedEx letter in an envelope.

00:32:28.658 --> 00:32:38.240
Diana opened it up and said all that stuff that I'm not going to say because I end up slipping and saying her name.

00:32:54.340 --> 00:32:55.379
But all that to be said, at that point I didn't know what to do as a father because I was just young and I was so scared to even call it autism.

00:32:55.379 --> 00:33:06.696
I'll never forget when my mom came and because in my mind I knew Megan wasn't doing very well at the time.

00:33:10.148 --> 00:33:14.120
My mom took me out to this Mexican restaurant and she said, "Brandon, I need to tell you something.

00:33:14.914 --> 00:33:18.826
" I remember looking at her thinking, "Well, what are you talking about?

00:33:18.826 --> 00:33:27.760
" She goes, "The family's been talking and we want to tell you we really believe that your Megan has autism.

00:33:48.583 --> 00:33:49.166
" I lost it.

00:33:49.166 --> 00:33:55.680
I'm talking, fear hit me like a 2x4 upside the head.

00:33:55.680 --> 00:33:57.500
It felt like that.

00:34:08.320 --> 00:34:08.848
I remember thinking I felt so betrayed at the time, so upset because it had gone on for so long.

00:34:08.848 --> 00:34:11.600
And people didn't know how to really address it.

00:34:12.239 --> 00:34:16.639
I guess my mom and dad didn't know how to really address it because I was just naive.

00:34:16.639 --> 00:34:24.559
First child, we didn't know what we were doing really.

00:34:24.559 --> 00:34:30.592
But we didn't realize how far behind Megan was and her not talking at three years old.

00:34:30.592 --> 00:34:43.440
What was over that and started looking at things and going through her development out of just ignorance.

00:34:52.399 --> 00:34:55.780
We didn't realize what was going on until family started shedding light on it because of my sister's kids.

00:34:55.780 --> 00:35:03.853
As I look back at those days, it was the hardest time of my life.

00:35:03.853 --> 00:35:26.400
But if it wasn't for the word of God, if it wasn't for knowing who I am in Christ, when I came home and started talking to Diana that night, she wept and wept and wept.

00:35:26.400 --> 00:35:47.040
We took her to a doctor and I can't even say his name because he was not.

00:35:47.040 --> 00:35:47.580
Dr.

00:35:47.580 --> 00:35:50.460
Edgington was his name and he was a neuropsychologist.

00:35:50.460 --> 00:35:50.880
Dr.

00:35:50.880 --> 00:35:55.696
Edgington and he was in Edmond, Oklahoma.

00:35:55.696 --> 00:36:01.540
He was only one of so many in the whole area.

00:36:01.540 --> 00:36:05.280
It took us forever to get in there.

00:36:05.280 --> 00:36:17.460
I'll never forget his report that first time he went in there and he evaluated her.

00:36:17.970 --> 00:36:26.600
I felt like somebody had just kicked the snot out of me.

00:36:37.240 --> 00:36:37.900
I walked away just weeping.

00:36:37.900 --> 00:36:41.851
So angry at the circumstance.

00:36:41.851 --> 00:36:44.416
So angry.

00:36:44.416 --> 00:37:01.140
So afraid because I didn't want anybody saying the word, because life and death is in the power of your tongue.

00:37:13.119 --> 00:37:13.959
I was so scared for anybody to say out of their mouth that Megan had autism because I didn't want them speaking it.

00:37:13.959 --> 00:37:18.594
I didn't want them to speak word curses.

00:37:36.744 --> 00:37:37.152
I didn't want to speak anything because I was so freaked out by the power of life and death in your tongue and speaking things over her.

00:37:49.440 --> 00:37:49.860
I wouldn't allow anybody to say anything.

00:37:49.860 --> 00:37:53.360
So does it sound flaky now?

00:37:53.360 --> 00:37:54.479
Yeah.

00:37:54.479 --> 00:37:57.794
Because of what I've walked through.

00:37:57.794 --> 00:38:05.413
There's so much that you feel like it's bondage.

00:38:06.799 --> 00:38:17.560
I look at it back and I say there's a lot of bondage in that.

00:38:17.560 --> 00:38:25.289
The way I had to come to the reality of what I was looking at.

00:38:25.289 --> 00:38:35.640
There was so much bondage, but God has brought us through is what I'm trying to tell you all.

00:38:35.640 --> 00:38:39.097
We're still seeing healing even today.

00:38:39.097 --> 00:38:46.613
We're seeing manifestations of her changing and yet she's in her 20s.

00:38:50.480 --> 00:39:10.320
And I'm going to say something that's very private, personal, but when she's getting ready to start her cycle now, she knows when she started and she'll get stuff to make sure she doesn't mess up the house.

00:39:10.320 --> 00:39:17.547
She knows now when her cycle has started and she goes and cleans herself up.

00:39:17.547 --> 00:39:24.942
If anybody understands a child with autism, that is a miracle in itself.

00:39:25.226 --> 00:40:04.795
And it took years of believing that she wouldn't play in her menses because it was stimulating for a child's special needs to play in their blood, or to do whatever to go through the hell that I feel like I have been through and teach her, "Honey, we don't do that.

00:40:04.795 --> 00:40:08.011
That's foul.

00:40:08.011 --> 00:40:16.820
" For her to stop that by the power of God.

00:40:16.820 --> 00:40:46.354
And when I went to a Billy Burke meeting, even this last time when we went in October to Eufaula and the power of God touched Megan, we've seen even more progress in her behavior.

00:40:46.354 --> 00:40:54.960
And he always talks about a sermon about the dove that went out and got a leaf on Noah's ark.

00:40:55.600 --> 00:40:56.240
You see Noah's ark behind us.

00:41:08.871 --> 00:41:09.226
We got the leaf.

00:41:33.959 --> 00:41:34.489
It went out, it came back, it had nothing.

00:41:34.489 --> 00:41:49.570
Then Noah let the dove out and it came back with a leaf, the little olive twig.

00:41:58.971 --> 00:41:59.703
That was the sign that the flood was over.

00:41:59.703 --> 00:42:08.153
Sometimes all you have is an olive piece.

00:42:08.153 --> 00:42:13.760
That's all the hope you may have.

00:42:26.720 --> 00:42:32.140
As the dove went out and found the flood was over, the first sign that the flood was over and that there was change coming, the olive leaf was right there.

00:42:32.140 --> 00:42:42.187
So Noah knew immediately that something is about to change.

00:42:42.187 --> 00:42:45.056
He laid hold to the olive leaf.

00:42:45.056 --> 00:42:47.771
That little bitty dove brought it back.

00:42:56.480 --> 00:42:57.056
And he knew that there was change coming.

00:42:57.056 --> 00:43:07.625
The flood is beginning to recede.

00:43:07.625 --> 00:43:30.560
So I know that there's a lot of people that maybe you just have that olive, that little bit of olive branch, a little olive leaf in the dove's mouth.

00:43:30.560 --> 00:43:36.579
That could be your circumstances in your life.

00:43:36.579 --> 00:43:50.729
Like I'm trying to tell you, Megan will all of a sudden when she starts, she'll know it's time to not have her lady panties on.

00:43:50.729 --> 00:43:54.880
It's time to go get her diaper on again.

00:44:07.519 --> 00:44:09.471
And to switch in her mind to know it's no longer panty time, it's diaper time so we don't make a mess.

00:44:09.471 --> 00:44:11.936
She does it by herself.

00:44:15.315 --> 00:44:15.697
I know this is very private, y'all.

00:44:15.697 --> 00:44:29.040
But it's something that is a miracle that's been going on for quite a while now since October.

00:44:36.160 --> 00:44:36.400
And sometimes you get those olive leaves and you realize the flood is receding.

00:44:36.400 --> 00:44:41.812
No matter what the doctor tries to tell you, the flood is receding.

00:44:41.812 --> 00:44:42.666
Don't lose hope.

00:44:42.666 --> 00:44:44.320
The flood is receding.

00:44:44.320 --> 00:44:53.991
Even if you just got a little olive leaf, even if you've got just a little change in your circumstances, hey, guess what?

00:44:53.991 --> 00:44:58.400
That's the beginning of the flood receding.

00:44:58.400 --> 00:45:02.927
Noah had to grab on to something.

00:45:30.655 --> 00:45:30.996
It was an olive twig or leaf.

00:45:40.960 --> 00:45:41.164
I believe it's a leaf.

00:45:43.973 --> 00:45:44.853
It was enough to fit in the beak of a dove.

00:45:52.000 --> 00:45:52.457
I know it's not a branch.

00:46:04.139 --> 00:46:04.409
It was a leaf.

00:46:04.409 --> 00:46:13.623
As you see Noah's ark behind me, that's the one I wanted because the Lord spoke to me.

00:46:22.379 --> 00:46:22.719
The leaf of your circumstances, the expiration date of your circumstances, is at hand.

00:46:22.719 --> 00:46:25.800
God is a God of miracles.

00:46:38.740 --> 00:46:39.080
The dove came to him in the evening, and lo, in her mouth was an olive leaf plucked off.

00:46:39.080 --> 00:46:46.640
So Noah knew that the waters were abated from the earth.

00:46:46.640 --> 00:46:57.855
Then the dove came to him in the evening, and behold, a freshly plucked olive leaf was in her mouth, and Noah knew that the water had receded from the earth.

00:46:57.855 --> 00:47:03.319
So whatever your olive leaf is, whatever your circumstance is, it may seem impossible.

00:47:03.319 --> 00:47:08.800
If you don't lose hope, your circumstances are going to change.

00:47:08.800 --> 00:47:13.040
Being fully persuaded, you go from believing to fully persuaded.

00:47:13.040 --> 00:47:19.184
I'm sure Noah was very discouraged, but an olive leaf gave him hope.

00:47:26.261 --> 00:47:26.486
I pray for you tonight to have hope and your breakthrough for whatever you're believing.

00:47:29.048 --> 00:47:31.697
It may not be something big because a little olive leaf is not big.

00:47:42.907 --> 00:47:43.173
It showed a sign.

00:47:43.173 --> 00:47:54.731
When you see your first breakthrough and manifestation, you realize I've kicked that devil in the teeth long enough.

00:47:54.731 --> 00:47:56.833
He's getting tired.

00:47:56.833 --> 00:48:01.840
I'm not giving up on what God has promised me.

00:48:01.840 --> 00:48:11.189
I'm thankful for the foundation of the word of God that will change you from the inside out.

00:48:13.440 --> 00:48:16.240
That will change us from glory to glory.

00:48:26.274 --> 00:48:26.617
The more you meditate on that word, it will change you from your insides out.

00:48:30.463 --> 00:48:33.536
I have learned to stand in my own circumstance with finances.

00:48:34.600 --> 00:48:40.799
The Lord said, I want you to take these things and teach my people.

00:48:46.319 --> 00:48:49.633
I tried to bring it so I could teach like I was teaching at Shoner Church.

00:48:50.545 --> 00:48:55.635
It doesn't have to be complicated.

00:49:01.160 --> 00:49:01.410
You don't have to be an amazing speaker.

00:49:01.410 --> 00:49:03.577
I've learned it is simple.

00:49:03.577 --> 00:49:12.788
If you make it simple where people grab on to it, that changes them.

00:49:12.788 --> 00:49:17.896
I'm simple, but in that, Jesus visits me.

00:49:17.896 --> 00:49:24.096
He doesn't look for perfection; he looks for a heart that is after him.

00:49:24.096 --> 00:49:30.240
If you needed somebody that spoke like a T.

00:49:30.240 --> 00:49:31.039
D.

00:49:31.039 --> 00:49:40.540
Jakes, that you have to bring a dictionary to church to understand, that's not Brandon.

00:49:40.540 --> 00:49:46.240
I hardly know how to speak big words.

00:50:15.903 --> 00:50:16.207
I have to say it is what it is because I barely finished high school.

00:50:16.207 --> 00:50:29.240
But God will take the foolish things of the world and do something huge in your life to confound the wise.

00:50:39.543 --> 00:50:39.874
He said, Brandon, I can take anybody and turn them into somebody.

00:50:51.646 --> 00:50:51.851
He can change your life if you lean into him.

00:50:51.851 --> 00:50:59.017
If you realize where I come from and where God blessed us now, you would be shocked.

00:51:06.729 --> 00:51:07.099
It's a lot to me because I come from nothing.

00:51:07.099 --> 00:51:26.720
From the janitor that made barely $17,000 a year, you look at where God has brought you and you say, Lord, you have done so much for me.

00:51:40.910 --> 00:51:41.080
I hope that blessed you.

00:51:41.080 --> 00:51:44.378
Now, let's talk about what the Lord said last night.

00:51:44.378 --> 00:51:50.500
There are so many of you that need to know what I believe is coming.

00:51:55.248 --> 00:51:55.392
I saw a storm last night against our ships.

00:51:55.392 --> 00:52:01.600
I saw that we would attack Iran in the days ahead.

00:52:21.586 --> 00:52:22.053
The Lord said to pray for our military bases in Kuwait and Baghdad.

00:52:22.053 --> 00:52:31.973
I saw our boats, but what was interesting, I saw surprise payloads full of biological weapons in these drones.

00:52:54.034 --> 00:52:54.503
As it went in, it sprayed the decks and the boats.

00:53:08.000 --> 00:53:09.739
I saw the troops on the bases with massive boils, convulsing with pain and agony.

00:53:31.165 --> 00:53:31.588
The air defense systems were not able to hold everything back.

00:53:45.368 --> 00:53:45.893
I saw a yellow-looking liquid in the wings of these drones.

00:53:57.120 --> 00:53:57.400
It was like a five-gallon bottle, like an Ozarka bottle, attached with a sprayer.

00:53:57.400 --> 00:54:01.059
The drone had a stealth look and was big.

00:54:02.559 --> 00:54:03.607
It was halfway full and sloshing around.

00:54:04.130 --> 00:54:07.119
It was spraying and releasing a fog on the people.

00:54:07.119 --> 00:54:10.730
I saw a plan coming out of Damascus.

00:54:10.730 --> 00:54:15.448
I saw Turkey and Syria coming together to come against Israel.

00:54:28.537 --> 00:54:28.823
The Lord said, pray over Jordan airspace.

00:54:37.239 --> 00:54:37.699
I saw another plot from Damascus, another biological attack in the night.

00:54:37.699 --> 00:54:49.220
There were weapons being given to Iran that were secret, coming on major planes in the middle of the night as a friendly pack.

00:54:49.220 --> 00:54:55.670
I saw these C-17s, these big planes that hold our tanks and military equipment.

00:54:58.919 --> 00:54:59.659
These massive planes, I saw two of them flying into Iran.

00:55:00.409 --> 00:55:04.079
They were giving them special weapons to defend themselves against America.

00:55:04.079 --> 00:55:15.275
China was involved; I saw it in the vision.

00:55:41.955 --> 00:55:42.684
It was very clear, and they have done it more than once.

00:55:42.684 --> 00:56:01.040
I saw them deliver this crate, which looked like a wooden crate, but it contained some kind of communication device that would send a signal to a satellite and somehow emit an electromagnetic pulse.

00:56:01.040 --> 00:56:12.034
It is not permanent, but I do not know how to describe it; I am trying to use my words.

00:56:12.034 --> 00:56:32.418
As it shot off, it was active for just enough time to disarm our battleship, but eventually, you could upload again and push the buttons to turn it back on.

00:56:50.526 --> 00:56:50.937
I do not know how else to describe this, but I saw this pulse, which looked like radio waves coming out of a satellite; these were secret weapons.

00:56:50.937 --> 00:56:53.008
God have mercy.

00:56:53.008 --> 00:56:56.079
So we pray over our troops.

00:57:00.049 --> 00:57:07.040
I am allowed to go over here now, so I will not say anything else about that.

00:57:23.359 --> 00:57:23.768
I saw Cuba, and as you heard Trump say about the regime change, I saw a dog backed into a corner.

00:57:39.577 --> 00:57:39.851
I saw the Castro people, the ones who have been dictators over Cuba for how long now?

00:57:39.851 --> 00:57:56.799
Even since Trump was a little boy, there has been a tyrant government since the 1960s, the Cuban missile crisis, and all the stuff going on over there.

00:57:59.920 --> 00:58:18.011
I saw this man backed into a corner, getting ready to have a regime change, but I heard the word about a new type of Hiroshima experiment, like we did when we dropped the atom bomb.

00:58:18.011 --> 00:58:46.903
I saw a retaliatory attack coming out of Cuba that was a surprise, as if to say, we have lost it all, there is nothing more I can do, and I am going down in a blaze of glory.

00:59:03.073 --> 00:59:03.325
That is what this crazy guy was doing.

00:59:03.325 --> 00:59:06.880
Now, can we change this in prayer?

00:59:20.106 --> 00:59:22.079
I believe we can, but I am telling you, what I saw was almost like an animal backed into a corner ready to retaliate.

00:59:33.464 --> 00:59:33.728
I saw some kind of weapon given to them by Russia.

00:59:36.346 --> 00:59:37.739
You need to remember this; I saw a weapon given to them by Russia.

00:59:42.480 --> 00:59:45.840
I do not know if this is a weapon of mass destruction, but it looked round and had a biohazard symbol on the side of it.

00:59:45.840 --> 00:59:56.720
It was under the ground; I saw this thing coming up and being used in the days ahead, and it was very catastrophic.

01:00:11.359 --> 01:00:13.319
I do not know if this is tactical or if it is like a briefcase; I have seen these briefcases that are radioactive.

01:00:21.839 --> 01:00:26.799
I have seen the green sides of it; it looks like a 1970s briefcase.

01:00:37.387 --> 01:00:37.591
I saw it, but this was different.

01:00:47.851 --> 01:00:48.023
The Lord showed me to pray for it.

01:01:00.823 --> 01:01:01.097
I saw Claudia—remember I told you she was dragging her nails because her time was up soon—dragging her fingers across the desk.

01:01:01.097 --> 01:01:17.359
Now, I believe this is a metaphor; I do not really think she is going to have cat-like nails.

01:01:37.502 --> 01:01:37.733
It is a vision; I am telling you what I saw.

01:01:37.733 --> 01:02:01.520
She was holding onto her desk and scraping it as two men had a hold of each leg, pulling her out of the office through her carpet, and she was scratching the whole way to the back of a paddy wagon, like when you transport prisoners in a jail car with bars.

01:02:08.869 --> 01:02:09.179
It looked like something the Joker would ride in; it had bars on the windows and was armored.

01:02:09.179 --> 01:02:13.618
They put her in the back of this.

01:02:13.618 --> 01:02:16.670
Now, is that a metaphor?

01:02:25.920 --> 01:02:26.240
I do not know.

01:02:26.240 --> 01:02:31.405
That is what I saw in a vision.

01:02:31.405 --> 01:02:36.470
But it looked like an armored truck.

01:02:36.470 --> 01:02:57.538
If you contend and you pray, the man that looks like Antonio Banderas—who looks like a Hollywood star, very handsome—is conservative, and this is who the Lord wants to be over Mexico.

01:03:02.079 --> 01:03:04.791
I saw a new man rising up and taking the baton, looking very classy in his suit and white shirt, like GQ.

01:03:09.393 --> 01:03:11.324
I saw this man rising up, and I saw revival breaking out in Mexico.

01:03:11.706 --> 01:03:24.177
But the Lord said again: you will have to contend, church, and pray for this; it will not just happen.

01:03:24.177 --> 01:03:29.249
I saw revival breaking out in Venezuela, Colombia, and Cuba.

01:03:30.857 --> 01:03:34.369
The Lord said, a major move of my presence is coming.

01:03:34.369 --> 01:03:37.680
They were placing Santeria around that Cuban man.

01:03:37.680 --> 01:03:52.932
Santeria was being placed around the man in Cuba, and they were using this demonic stuff to protect him; they were trying to perform some kind of cultic ritual around this man.

01:04:03.500 --> 01:04:12.498
The Lord showed me this, but I saw a major move, and the Lord said he is bringing that to naught and setting the people free from satanic practice, for a satanic stronghold has been on the whole island.

01:04:12.729 --> 01:04:21.920
The Lord said he was bringing that satanic stronghold down in Venezuela, Colombia, and Mexico.

01:04:21.920 --> 01:04:46.040
He said, I am going to bring a great revival all over South America, and a flood of my presence is going to bring in the greatest harvest of souls this world has ever seen.

01:04:46.040 --> 01:04:51.420
They had their day, and it is done.

01:04:51.420 --> 01:04:57.344
First Corinthians 5:5 is coming to full fruition, a great manifestation of the glory.

01:04:57.344 --> 01:05:00.525
He said, I am dealing with Cuba.

01:05:09.543 --> 01:05:10.011
I saw brand new sanctions being lifted and economic growth coming around the island.

01:05:15.706 --> 01:05:20.440
Can we stop the retaliation if this man leaves and says he does not want to lose his life and backs out?

01:05:20.440 --> 01:05:26.080
Yes, I believe that.

01:05:26.080 --> 01:05:28.949
That is the power of prayer.

01:05:28.949 --> 01:05:37.249
Can he just resign, bring in a new leader, and ride away on his horse?

